{"tid":1221880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"利用更多輿論讓身邊人了解逃犯條例，推動佢地一齊參與616反送中遊行。","createTime":"2019-06-14T10:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T10:10:11.000Z","uid":260169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2361635e7ee0294d74089bfd4b45f46b0fbb4a35","tid":1221880,"uid":260169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jp9M6vc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjp9M6vc.png&h=e05122f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好讓自己或者朋友好似建制派遊行咁，出黎唔知為咩！！利用輿論朋友間對話講解更多逃犯條例。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反送中</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/bills/b201903291.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr18-19%2Fchinese%2Fbills%2Fb201903291.pdf&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=dce92183\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/bills/b201903291.pdf</a><br />\n保住103萬反送中市民對於遊行ge決心<br />\n市民之間唔好分化唔好撕裂！<br />\n有共同目標，首先係政府！<br />\n每一個市民支持反送中都係重要的，記得係每一個。唔好過多標籤！出黎行就係為香港，就係香港人！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">616反送中</span><br />\n俾建制派知道，市民就係了解所以出黎，未行出黎個班先係真正未了解！"},{"pid":"5e85b3c9f61dd213bc0fe8580145217c1d758938","tid":1221880,"uid":260169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:10:11.000Z","msg":"推"}]}